## Invest in Eternal Impact

Your financial support of Bear Lake Camp helps provide life-changing experiences for young people and adults who might not otherwise have the opportunity to attend camp or retreat.

- $50 provides one day of camp for a camper
- $175 covers half of a week for a camper needing assistance
- $350 fully sponsors a camper for a week

{% ctaButton
