## Volunteer & Give by Mail

There are many ways to support Bear Lake Camp beyond financial giving. Volunteer your time and skills, or send a gift by mail.

Send your tax-deductible gift to:

**Bear Lake Camp**
**1805 S. 16th St.**
**Albion, IN 46701**

Make checks payable to "Bear Lake Camp."
